id":"ea5e053bfdf064662cfa5d8058474fe4e786026b","tid":1280020,"uid":237175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T23:45:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46718f3475399ca881b1682569f6e1429cd77697","tid":1280020,"uid":139919,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T23:46:20.000Z","msg":"有兄弟想自殺！請幫手阻止！<br />\n<br />\n1. 男性（睇筆法似，男仔名）<br />\n2. 黑衫 （運動象徵）<br />\n3. 長袖衫/褲 （用黎遮傷口）<br />\n4. 口罩 （都係遮傷口）<br />\n5. 行動可能有些少不便（中過彈）<br />\n6.30歲左右<br />\n<br />\n如果佢想仿效梁烈士，佢可能會帶<br />\na. 橫額<br />\nb. 大字報<br />\nc. 黃雨衣<br />\nd. 塗鴉用具<br />\n<br />\n手足好可能係用緊sony電話，證據係佢cap screen個volte icon<br />\n<br />\n留意下身邊既人有無袋，個袋似唔似放上面既野，必要時說明苦衷大膽問可疑人士開袋黎睇下<br />\n<br />\n以上特徵中越多，機會越高。各位加油，天佑香港！"},{"pid":"60006781783e9004de4750d0fb868c9a46d8539c","tid":1280020,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T23:47:02.000Z","msg":"唔好啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a736b9d1d76eace7ee70ed3b4c32d3d04c9a78eb","tid":1280020,"uid":112974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T23:49:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c78bdcd17463d3c8cb1c25fba5445f1b6c491eb9","tid":1280020,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T23:51:31.000Z","msg":"死唔可以解決問題 留返條命仔繼續為不公義而抗爭唔係更好咩 對唔住啊 當我求下你唔好啦 巴打 唔希望再有人有事 希望佢唔好咁做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定唔可以有事 一個都不能少"},{"pid":"73f96e083e2b9fd4a188f6e516195a66347b59ae","tid":1280020,"uid":59804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T23:52:36.000Z","msg":"推呀 好似會去pp跳"},{"pid":"e3661345f94e2763a18dbdc03c86c47a7e5a9407","tid":1280020,"uid":59804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T23:54:58.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c951ee2a968b76daf09f60ac9abdea1e53f0587f","tid":1280020,"uid":222723,"like":0